---
description: Frontend rules for Vite-built bundle assets
globs:
  - "src/Resources/assets/**/*.ts"
  - "vite.config.ts"
  - "package.json"
alwaysApply: false
---

Prefer:
- strict TypeScript where used
- preserving the Vite IIFE entry (`tiptap-editor.ts` → `src/Resources/public/tiptap-editor.js`)
- English JSDoc for exported helpers

Avoid committing unrelated generated blobs; rebuild with `pnpm run build` when sources change.
